title: Am I Stalled Or Am I Fooling Myself?
itunes:title: Am I Stalled Or Am I Fooling Myself?
description:
Today's podcast is all about how to know when you're really on a weightloss plateau.
 
We talk about what a plateau really is, how you evaluate it, and what to do to get the weightloss kickstarted again.
 
We also talk about what a plateau isn't, and I coach Kathy on seeing the difference and how to stop blaming the things happening around her for her overeating.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
